org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview
Class AeProcessDefToWebVisitorBase

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview.AeProcessDefToWebVisitorBase
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDefVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeProcessDefToWebModelVisitor, AeProcessWebPropertyBuilder
public class AeProcessDefToWebVisitorBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeDefVisitor

Base visitor responsible for building the web visual model or definition properties. The visit methods in this class are empty. Subclasses should override these methods when needed.
